title: Match of the Day 2 - 28th September 2014 - HDTV X264
description:
SPORT: Match of the Day 2
On: BBC 1 HD
Date: Sunday 28th September 2014
Time: 22:30 to 23:20

Mark Chapman introduces highlights of the day's Premier League meeting between
West Brom and Burnley, plus a look back at all the action from Saturday's
matches. The Premier League has never featured a meeting between these sides -
newly promoted Burnley hope the first clash ends with a Clarets victory. The
Baggies are equally keen to secure the spoils having spent the last season at
the wrong end of the Premier League table, only narrowly avoiding relegation.
There is also a look back at a busy Saturday in the Premier League, which
featured a derby double with Liverpool taking on Everton and Arsenal facing
north London neighbours Tottenham.

Sorry it's late, I was watching the baggies and fell asleep :D
